  "title": "Marketing Intern",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>• Assist in coordinating exports and perform export administrative documentation.</p>\n<p>• Support the team to brainstorm, develop, and execute marketing or branding campaigns.</p>\n<p>• Writing clear content to promote our products/services.</p>\n<p>• Plan, coordinate and handle all trade shows and major promotions and assist in all sales and marketing activities.</p>\n<p>• Assist in designing marketing collaterals for target audiences across all multimedia and social media platforms.</p>\n<p>• Coordinate schedules and timelines on the calendar for marketing campaigns and project phases with various departments.</p>\n<p>• To perform such other duties / work as directed by the Company from time to time.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>• Candidate must be enrolled in at least a Diploma, Bachelor's Degree or equivalent course</p>\n<p>• Meticulous and well-organised, able to work independently</p>",
